登時不時都有啲5p字或者係度Ching Ching 架啦<br />\nBlock撚晒佢咪得囉 <br />\n只要大多數人都保良正字既嘅優良傳統<br />\n呢啲垃圾自然就會收皮<br />\n<br />\n我覺得根本影響唔到lihkg既發展</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撚樣既比例太大就係問題"},{"pid":"5acf71910bd6463f10875b4ba14b2d3443bd7390","tid":31281,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>例如：<br />\nChing -&amp;gt; 巴打<br />\n甘 -&amp;gt; 咁<br />\n碎 -&amp;gt; 歲<br />\n禾 - &amp;gt;我<br />\n<br />\n咁就減少晒啲紛爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing變巴打 work<br />\n<br />\n有幾何打英文，有既自己加個space 啦"},{"pid":"a900104c65783669e01333e0d144e8d62f20dd1f","tid":31281,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔搞掂呢個問題<br />\n人只會不斷咁流失<br />\n變為第二個膠登</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感覺部分係專登入來搞事"},{"pid":"ce0aa9258a1aa5917c996382b1e58d17968e75e7","tid":31281,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不咁心<br />\n鋤我日當午<br />\n<br />\n唔掂喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 秒殺</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195046b90f1a9b971df244ca42a9406c9aed2132","tid":31281,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不咁心<br />\n鋤我日當午<br />\n<br />\n唔掂喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 秒殺</blockquote><br 